---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
  <BaseLayout>
      <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
        Effective date: February 24, 2026<br><br>
        <br>
        This Cookie Policy explains how EddiesGames uses cookies and similar technologies.<br>
        <br>
        What are cookies?<br>
        Cookies are small text files stored on your device. Similar technologies include local storage, pixels, and device identifiers.<br>
        <br>
        Types of cookies we may use<br>
        <br>
        Essential cookies:<br>
        Used for basic site functionality and security.<br>
        <br>
        Analytics cookies:<br>
        Help us understand how visitors use the site (e.g., which games are most played) so we can improve.<br>
        <br>
        Advertising cookies (if ads are enabled):<br>
        Used by advertising partners to deliver, measure, and personalize ads.<br>
        <br>
        Managing cookies<br>
        You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may impact some site functionality.<br>
        <br>
        If we run ads, you may also be able to manage ad personalization through the ad provider’s settings.<br>
        <br>
        Updates:<br>
        We may update this policy as the site evolves.<br>
        <br>
        Contact:<br>
        support@eddiesgames.xyz<br>
  </BaseLayout>